'From Squeak3.6beta of ''4 July 2003'' [latest update: #5387] on 9 August 2003 at 11:04:53 pm'!"Change Set:		CanvasCharacterScannerFixDate:			9 August 2003Author:			Masashi UmezawaIn 5279TrueTypeTextStyle-yo , CanvasCharacterScanner>>setFont refers to defaultTextColor. But defaultTextColor is sometimes nil, which causes displaying problems. Now defaultTextColor will be set to 'Color black' if it is nil."!!CanvasCharacterScanner methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'mu 8/9/2003 22:40'!defaultTextColor	defaultTextColor ifNil:[defaultTextColor _ Color black].	^defaultTextColor! !!CanvasCharacterScanner methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'mu 8/9/2003 22:40'!setFont	foregroundColor _ self defaultTextColor.	super setFont.	destY _ lineY + line baseline - font ascent! !